      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DARCY DAKOTA (1) ran below his best last time finishing sixth (22.11) over 390m at this track in a Free For All. Form at the trip sound including 27 wins. Goes very well from this draw with five wins and two minor placings from eight starts. Looks the one to beat on his best form. HARA'S NEO (2) was well off top last time, finishing 6th (20.49) in a Grade 4/5 at Capalaba. Great record here at the trip having never missed the frame including nine wins. Form from her last run is proving strong. One of the main contenders. WESTERN LIES (7) was prominent throughout when winning two back but could manage only midfield last time when 4th and beaten 4.5 lengths at Casino (23.91). Goes very well from this draw with four wins and two minor placings from nine starts. Has ability and can measure up. OXIDISATION (4) won last start after racing on the pace. Big chance on that form.",
